Allianz Says Italy Crisis Not Based on Fundamentals, FTD Says

-- B y   C o r n e l i u s   R a h n
-- 
2011-07-17T15:27:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-17/allianz-says-italy-crisis-not-based-on-fundamentals-ftd-says.html
Allianz SE (ALV)  Chief Financial Officer
Paul Achleitner said the decline in Italian  government bonds  is
“not justified by fundamental data” and will be resolved once
a solution is found for  Greece ,  Financial Times Deutschland 
reported, citing an interview.  Allianz holds 28 billion euros ($39.6 billion) of Italian
bonds, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Cornelius Rahn in Frankfurt at 
 crahn2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kenneth Wong in Berlin at 
 kwong11@bloomberg.net  